They'll visit restaurants, markets, food trucks and stands to get a taste of the local flavor and use that inspiration to create an easy meal for the family.




Extra Virgin Americana - Season 1, Episode 1



Fear and Cooking in the Grand Canyon

On the way to the Grand Canyon, Debi Mazar, Gabriele Corcos and family stop to pick local ingredients at Agritopia, eat where the locals do at Liberty Market, and attempt to fill their RV at one of the oldest gas stations around. Once they arrive at the Canyon, they take in the views and enjoy a delicious meal.
